@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (0.70 / v0)
    tmp = (v2 - 0.23)
    tmp = ((tmp * v1) / wp.abs(wp.exp(v2 + 0.42)))
    v2 = 0.43
    v0 = wp.abs(tmp)
    v2 = wp.cos(((v2 + 0.77 * v1 + 0.58) + (v1 + 0.55 * tmp + 0.39)))
    tmp = wp.sin(0.88)
    v1 = ((wp.cos(v2 + 0.50) + 0.25) * v1)
    data[tid] = v0
